sellerCard.description: Greetings! I am Suhaib, a dedicated full-time WordPress website designer and developer. With a remarkable 7 years of experience and nearly 650 completed projects on Fiverr, I specialize in creating WordPress websites that enable businesses to reach their maximum potential. Let's connect to discuss your upcoming project, and I assure you that I will assist you in every possible way!

description.content:
Looking for a skilled person to do a WordPress website design and website development for you? Look no further! 


Being a perfect WordPress developer, I can create a fully functional website that is both visually appealing and user-friendly. Also, I understand the importance of creating a site that not only looks great but also performs well. That's why I pay close attention to every detail of the design and development process to ensure that your site meets your expectations and the needs of your target audience.



WHAT YOU GET


  • Professional design and development
  • Clean, modern, and responsive WordPress website (Desktop, tablet, and mobile)
  • Tailored design: Customizable colors, fonts, backgrounds, and more to ensure the uniqueness of the design.
  • Streamlined functionality: Basic SEO and fast loading
  • Social media integration
  • Licensed theme and builders (Elementor pro, Astra Pro, and more)
  • Stock images included
  • Valid revision until you are satisfied with the design
  • 14-28 days of free support after project completion
  • Comprehensive management guide after completion


In addition to these benefits, you will receive all the features outlined in each of the WordPress service plans.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What things do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will need your hosting or WordPress login details, as well as any branding materials you have available, such as your logo, color scheme, and font preferences. Additionally, you will need to provide the website content, including text, images, and any other media.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I don't have Images for my website will you provide them?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If you do not have images for your website, I can provide stock images that are relevant to your website's content. However, please note that if you have specific image requirements or would like custom images, then you need to provide or outsource them.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many Revisions do you offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The number of revisions included in your plan may vary. However, I always aim to provide valid revisions until the client is satisfied with the work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide any additional support after the completion of project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: After the completion of the project, you will receive a certain number of weeks of free support, depending on the plan you choose. Typically, 2-4 weeks of support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: After Website is done can I manage my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: With my user-friendly approach to website design, you'll find it easy to update your website content on your own. Additionally, I provide a video guide that walks you through the content update process, ensuring that you feel confident in managing your website moving forward.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you use licensed themes and plugins?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I never use unlicensed themes and plugins. Using nulled products is not only unethical but also unsafe for your website. I always use licensed themes and plugins to ensure the safety and security of your website.

I'd highly recommend Naikoo and definitely work with him again in the future!
